===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# {{context|now|_|rare}} Pertaining to someone learning the alphabet or basic studies; [[elementary]]; [[rudimentary]]. {{defdate|from 17th c.}}
# Pertaining to the alphabet, or several alphabets.{{defdate|from 17th c.}}
#*'''1971''', {{w|Brian Lumley}}, ‘Rising with Surtsey’:
